# Personal Context Index

This is the top-level map of Samson Schirmer's personal context portfolio. Agents should read this file first, then drill into the specific pages needed for the task.

## Core Profile

- [Identity](identity) — who Samson is, what he does, and the through-line across work and personal projects
- [Role & Responsibilities](role-and-responsibilities) — what his weeks look like and what he produces
- [Current Projects](current-projects) — active workstreams, personal projects, status, and success signals
- [Goals & Priorities](goals-and-priorities) — current goals, tradeoffs, and what is deliberately not prioritized
- [Preferences & Constraints](preferences-and-constraints) — working preferences, family constraints, energy patterns, and AI output preferences
- [Communication Style](communication-style) — how Samson writes, how he wants writing to sound, and audience-specific shifts
- [Team & Relationships](team-and-relationships) — key collaborators, stakeholders, and communication dynamics
- [Tools & Systems](tools-and-systems) — work platforms, personal stack, and integration principles
- [Domain Knowledge](domain-knowledge) — expertise, beginner areas, and mental models
- [Decision Log](decision-log) — decision-making style and durable strategic choices

