## Agent Usage

For any substantial task, start with the smallest relevant set of files. If the task touches Samson's professional work, read `identity`, `current-projects`, `goals-and-priorities`, and `communication-style`. If the task involves stakeholders, add `team-and-relationships`. If the task involves AI tooling or architecture, add `tools-and-systems` and `domain-knowledge`.
